(This project is an intelligent network traffic monitoring and analysis system. It captures) Tj
0 -14 Td
(live packets from the machine or network interface, stores normalized traffic records in) Tj
0 -14 Td
(SQLite, analyzes the captured data with multiple detection layers, groups suspicious) Tj
0 -14 Td
(findings into manageable incidents, and exposes the results through a Flask dashboard and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(reporting UI.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
