0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(It helps answer questions like:) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- What traffic is happening right now?) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Which hosts are most active?) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Which domains are being contacted?) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Is any host scanning ports?) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Is there burst traffic that looks like denial-of-service behavior?) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Are there repeated failed connections that suggest brute force or blocked access attempts?) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Is the current traffic pattern unusual compared to previously observed windows?) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
